text: The Rumyantsev Case () is a 1956 Russian crime drama movie directed by Iosif Kheifits and starring Aleksey Batalov, Sergey Lukyanov, Vladimir Lepko, Yevgeny Leonov, Inna Makarova, Nikolay Kryuchkov, Ants Eskola. ==Other websites== * Category:1956 crime drama movies Category:Russian crime movies Category:Russian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Iosif Kheifits
title: The Rumyantsev Case
